    "millsfield:images_texts": [
      "Along the way of TWA...\nOAK CREEK CANYON\nАнізона\nRising high above\nthe desert floor,\nthe yellow, white and red\nrock formations of\nOak Creek Canyon\nare among Arizona's\nmost magnificent sights.\nThe Great Southwest is\nserved by fast, frequent\nTWA flights to Phoenix.\nUse your camera - remember your trip with pictures.\nTWA\nTRANS WORLD AIRLINES\nU.S.A. • EUROPE\nAFRICA • ASIA",
